					<outline text="- `rssnet.html` added to deploy folder"/>
					</outline>
				<outline text="#### 4/14/26; v0.4.1 by Claude">
					<outline text="- Used `__dirname` to resolve config and data paths À¸À¸À¸ wrong approach, reverted"/>
					<outline text="- Moved `pathServerHomePageSource` into code À¸À¸À¸ wrong approach, reverted"/>
